Usage: report_clock_gating_check [-help] [<object_list>] [-view <view_name>]
                                 [> <file_name>] [>> <file_name>]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>         # Specifies the pin/port list for which clock gating
                      # check is to be reported. (string, optional)
-view <view_name>     # View for which clock gating check is to be reported.
                      # Default is worst of all views (string, optional)
> <file_name>         # Redirect output to file (redirect_operator, optional)
>> <file_name>        # Redirect output to file (redirect_operator, optional)